        "plotImpact": "Eirik returns to the Rangers' Command Post with the injured Kira, seeking medical attention and reporting the dire situation at the Ambush Site. This strengthens the party's connection with Commander Elen and sets the stage for further investigation of the bandit threat."
      }
    }
  ]
}
